guys, we didn't mean
to be that mean. I mean --

00:07:12,432 --> 00:07:15,235
no, because the wrong
evaluation -- it's too
bad you did that.
yeah.

00:07:15,235 --> 00:07:16,836
Okay.
Yeah, I apologize for us --
the initial response.

00:07:16,836 --> 00:07:18,905
I didn't expect it.
All of us here tried
it, except for Kevin.

00:07:18,905 --> 00:07:20,340
What are you
apologizing for?

00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:21,975
Because we try to be very
supportive entrepreneurs.

