strikes the perfect balance

00:09:24,664 --> 00:09:26,032
between fun
and physicality

00:09:26,032 --> 00:09:28,535
with our award-winning courses
and our day-long festival.

00:09:28,535 --> 00:09:31,738
So which one of you sharks
